      <title>马来西亚反对党向议会致函，寻求补选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/malaysia-opposition-sends-note-to-parliament-seeks-by-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚反对党寻求在其前成员占据的六个议会选区举行补选，此举有可能使总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣 (Anwar Ibrahim) 的改革计划失去支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/malaysia-opposition-sends-note-to-parliament-seeks-by-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 05:14:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾立法者投票扩大权力，无视总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/taiwan-lawmakers-vote-to-expand-their-powers-defying-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾立法者再次投票决定扩大传唤公职人员的权力，无视抗议者和总统赖清德的反对。预计赖清德将请求宪法法院审查这些修改并暂停实施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/taiwan-lawmakers-vote-to-expand-their-powers-defying-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 04:18:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>放弃纸币使瑞典成为数字犯罪分子的避风港</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/sweden-led-europe-s-move-to-cashless-economy-now-it-faces-soaring-fraud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这个北欧国家在欧洲率先推行无现金支付，但快速简便的数字商务使消费者和国家容易受到欺诈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/sweden-led-europe-s-move-to-cashless-economy-now-it-faces-soaring-fraud</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 04:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙提前大选赌博令巴黎金融中心地位面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/what-the-french-snap-elections-mean-for-paris-s-role-as-finance-hub</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙在任期内花了大量时间劝说银行家和基金经理在英国脱欧后涌向巴黎。他决定提前举行大选，这可能会让一些业内人士感到不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/what-the-french-snap-elections-mean-for-paris-s-role-as-finance-hub</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟部队称，抵御胡塞武装需要增加一倍舰队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/fending-off-houthis-requires-double-the-fleet-eu-force-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟部署在红海保护船只的海军部队负责人表示，由于伊朗支持的胡塞叛军的袭击不断升级，该部队的规模需要增加一倍以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/fending-off-houthis-requires-double-the-fleet-eu-force-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Currys 首席执行官警告工党，飙升的最低工资会损害创造就业机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/minimum-wage-rises-hurt-job-creation-currys-ceo-warns-labour</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Currys Plc 首席执行官亚历克斯·巴尔多克 (Alex Baldock) 表示，英国新政府应确保最低工资的提高不会使雇用更多工人的成本过高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/minimum-wage-rises-hurt-job-creation-currys-ceo-warns-labour</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜军队第三次越界 韩国鸣枪警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/south-korea-fires-warning-shots-after-third-border-breach-by-north-s-troops</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜军队越过边界后撤退，韩国士兵开枪警告，这是本月在朝鲜半岛发生的第三起此类事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/south-korea-fires-warning-shots-after-third-border-breach-by-north-s-troops</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 03:25:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称中国应解释贸易数据异常加剧的原因</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/china-should-explain-growing-anomaly-in-trade-numbers-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部表示，中国海关数据显示，中国的贸易顺差远高于其国际收支报告的贸易顺差，北京应该澄清为何会出现这样的数字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/china-should-explain-growing-anomaly-in-trade-numbers-us-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 03:24:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>继美国和欧盟采取行动后，加拿大准备对中国电动汽车征收关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/canada-prepares-potential-tariffs-on-china-electric-vehicles-after-us-eu-moves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的政府正准备对中国制造的电动汽车征收新的关税，以使加拿大与美国和欧盟采取的行动保持一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/canada-prepares-potential-tariffs-on-china-electric-vehicles-after-us-eu-moves</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 23:27:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦穆斯林暴徒因涉嫌亵渎宗教杀害游客</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-20/a-muslim-mob-in-pakistan-torches-a-police-station-and-lynches-a-man-after-accusing-him-of-blasphemy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦白沙瓦（美联社）——周四，巴基斯坦西北部一群穆斯林暴徒闯入一家警察局，抓走一名被关押在那里的男子，然后将他私刑处死，罪名是他亵渎了伊斯兰教的圣书《古兰经》。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-20/a-muslim-mob-in-pakistan-torches-a-police-station-and-lynches-a-man-after-accusing-him-of-blasphemy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 20:25:58 GMT</pubDate>
